Gmail api is a restful api 
>allows to read and send emails.

Terms used in gmail api 
Message
Has the sender,receipients,subject and the body.
>Once message is created it cannot be editted or changed.
Represented by the message resource.

Thread 
>A collection of related messages forming a conversation.

Label.
A mechanism for organizing messages and threads.
>System labels
    -INBOX
    -TRASH
    -SPAM

>user labels
    -Represented by the label resource.

>Draft
    -Unsent message
    -A message contained within draft cannot be modified but can be replaced
    -uses the draft resource

